entry.value: ALTER TABLE ztm_buses_raw ADD IF NOT EXISTS PARTITION (dt='${dt}', hr='${hr}') LOCATION '/user/bigdata/data/parquet/ztm_buses_raw/${partition_path}';

CREATE EXTERNAL TABLE IF NOT EXISTS ztm_buses_raw ( Lines STRING, Lon DOUBLE, VehicleNumber STRING, Time BIGINT, Lat DOUBLE, Brigade STRING, ingest_time BIGINT ) PARTITIONED BY (dt STRING, hr STRING) STORED AS PARQUET LOCATION '/user/bigdata/data/parquet/ztm_buses_raw';
